summary.purpose: Barrel file that aggregates and re-exports all interface definitions from the interfaces sub-module.
summary.problem_solved: Provides a single import point for all platform interfaces so consumers do not need to know which specific file within interfaces/ defines each type.

internal.why_used: Re-exports core domain interfaces: TimestampType, firebase_timestamp, Site, NxUser, MobileAppUser, GoUser, Client, Board, Peripheral, Car, UnitExtra, UsersUnits, LastLocationCar, CarState, CanbusParameter, Equipment, EquipmentOption, EventFromDevice, EventFromDevice_Ruptela, EventFromDevice_Erm, ErmStates, ReportMeta, ReportMetaHeader, ReportMetaDataType, ReportParameterDataType, ReportDataRow, GprsItem
Re-exports credit management types: CreditType, CreditItem, CreditAuditAction, CreditAuditItem
Re-exports Go mobile app types: GoMobileUserRole, GoAuthModel, GoUserRole, GoCarLink, RoleInToken, GoUserCar

exports.name: global (re-export)
exports.description_one_line: Re-exports all core domain interfaces from interfaces/global.ts

exports.name: credits (re-export)
exports.description_one_line: Re-exports credit management types from interfaces/credits.ts

exports.description_one_line: Re-exports Go mobile app types from interfaces/go.ts

symbols.name: global (re-export)
symbols.description_one_line: Barrel re-export of all core domain interfaces from interfaces/global.ts

details.what_it_does: Publishes TimestampType, firebase_timestamp, Site, NxUser, MobileAppUser, GoUser, Client, Board, Peripheral, Car, UnitExtra, UsersUnits, LastLocationCar, CarState, CanbusParameter, Equipment, EquipmentOption, EventFromDevice, EventFromDevice_Ruptela, EventFromDevice_Erm, ErmStates, ReportMeta, ReportMetaHeader, ReportMetaDataType, ReportParameterDataType, ReportDataRow, and GprsItem through the interfaces barrel.

minimal_correct.title: Import a core interface through the interfaces barrel
minimal_correct.code:
import type { Car, Client } from 'akeyless-types-commons';
// Both are available because interfaces/index.ts re-exports interfaces/global.ts
